{"tid":477043,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"直到而家 我都係忘記唔到","createTime":"2017-11-22T14:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T17:26:52.000Z","uid":153118,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5dc444d6cf28b4d00b5cbff6a2f0b9363231dbd4","tid":477043,"uid":153118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"由分手到而家 都有成半年啦<br />\n同左佢一齊有半年<br />\n過往一齊經歷嘅 一點一滴都仲係腦入面<br />\n即使好小嘅事情 到而家都好印象深刻<br />\n冇左佢 係生活裹面 真係慢慢變得一事無成<br />\n唔識同人溝通 接觸 互動<br />\n我 會唔會唔再係我呢<br />\n或者 我真係仲未企得返起身<br />\n唉<br />\n今個聖誕 真係凍左好多"},{"pid":"3713b7e82143fba6d838736e85b2753e5e6f0275","tid":477043,"uid":136637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:06:01.000Z","msg":"姐姐俾啲溫暖你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793a175e3df0d1925a20a578a9b1692482e35738","tid":477043,"uid":146299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:14:02.000Z","msg":"半年就傷心成噉，十年果D點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375b4b75b200436230bed003bd70240f761d5d47","tid":477043,"uid":153118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>半年就傷心成噉，十年果D點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以都唔敢再有下一次 但又好想身邊有個人 好矛盾<br />\n又好想佢返黎我身邊"},{"pid":"73d770b71aa285f5752c5855c7341c358780935f","tid":477043,"uid":153118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:20:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姐姐俾啲溫暖你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係愛呀 哈利"},{"pid":"d7792e090206097edefd9bb8fe51ad9bb0fd10d2","tid":477043,"uid":43460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:35:38.000Z","msg":"分散自己注意力 <br />\n搵多啲興趣做<br />\n好快就會忘記"},{"pid":"477919d1ff9037d99e023f7b9aa8b73ec6568c10","tid":477043,"uid":124535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:36:43.000Z","msg":"兩個月都可以好深，唔關一齊幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似係"},{"pid":"51a46ffd45dfd70d7710c6c9b70a8d9fd40b026b","tid":477043,"uid":124535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:37:28.000Z","msg":"我都用左兩年時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油"},{"pid":"6e4a4e6f6ac1e0a5e273636c8b73c63453f9445d","tid":477043,"uid":153118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:41:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分散自己注意力 <br />\n搵多啲興趣做<br />\n好快就會忘記</blockquote><br />\n我都想呀<br />\n但每當去到一個同佢行過嘅街道<br />\n聽到佢中意聽嘅歌<br />\n佢中意嘅動物<br />\n好小好小野 都勾返起回憶"},{"pid":"83b409d27031d5c3ae3751c7e96441bffee2ec32","tid":477043,"uid":153118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:42:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都用左兩年時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油</blockquote><br />\n你戈排點去放低"},{"pid":"4fd4037758b7cd1acaa39524ec6e194a7048189d","tid":477043,"uid":76951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:47:29.000Z","msg":"我都係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都3個幾月了<br />\n近排又掛住返佢, 諗好多野<br />\n就考試, 冇心機溫<br />\n唉, 個心有d亂"},{"pid":"1c6aaf92d28366679cfa62261424d666a0157301","tid":477043,"uid":153118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:52:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都3個幾月了<br />\n近排又掛住返佢, 諗好多野<br />\n就考試, 冇心機溫<br />\n唉, 個心有d亂</blockquote><br />\n真係好冇動力<br />\n一齊加油呀bro"},{"pid":"e37346f2d43104dcaec05a74dd41b285bbb864c5","tid":477043,"uid":124535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T16:24:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都用左兩年時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油</blockquote><br />\n你戈排點去放低</blockquote><br />\n返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有得ot就o<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dea